Welcome to Luxfer Group
Luxfer Group is a global materials technology company specializing in the design, manufacture and supply of high-performance materials, components and gas cylinders to customers in a broad range of growing end markets.
            










Innovative Solutions...
Our aim is to develop close collaborative relationships with our customers to find innovative solutions to their needs for advanced materials, components and gas containment. Our focus is on demanding applications where our technical know-how and manufacturing expertise can combine to deliver a superior product.
            










High Growth Markets...
We target the ‘environmental´, ‘healthcare´ and ‘protection´ sectors, as we identified these as having the strongest potential to generate incremental profitable growth for our materials and/or gas containment technologies.
            
















