Contrasting Luxfer Holdings PLC (NYSE:LXFR) & U.S. Silica Holdings (SLCA)


					Posted by Oliver Carreras on Jul 21st, 2017 // No Comments




Luxfer Holdings PLC (NYSE: LXFR) and U.S. Silica Holdings (NYSE:SLCA) are both industrial products companies, but which is the superior investment? We will compare the two companies based on the strength of their dividends, risk, profitabiliy, institutional ownership, analyst recommendations, earnings and valuation. 
